OL,3,CPolice officers committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when arrested man died in
OL,5,Cpolice van
OL,7,FTwo officers from Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice committed gross misconduct by
OL,9,Ffailing to provide emergency first aid
OL,10,Fto a man who died after collapsing in
OL,11,Fthe back of their police van, a
OL,12,Fdisciplinary panel has found.
OL,14,FPCs Grant Mackenzie and Dean Hunkin
OL,15,Ftransported Stephen Reardon in the
OL,16,Fvan's secure holding area for almost
OL,17,F40 minutes after his arrest for
OL,18,Fdriving under the influence of drink
OL,19,For drugs in St Austell on 13 July,
OL,20,F2023.
