OL,3,CPolice officers committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when arrested man died in
OL,5,Cpolice van
OL,7,FMr Reardon slumped to the floor just
OL,8,Fminutes into the 17-mile trip to
OL,9,FNewquay Police Station and van CCTV
OL,10,Fshowed him suffering seizures and
OL,11,Fvisibly trembling.
OL,13,FAn investigation by the Independent
OL,14,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC)
OL,15,Frevealed the officers failed to spot
OL,16,Fthe 34-year-old needed urgent medical
OL,17,Fattention.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
