OL,5,Cpolice van
OL,7,FMr Reardon was found unconscious and
OL,8,Fnot breathing in the police station
OL,9,Fcar park at 11.23am. He was given CPR
OL,10,Fand paramedics attended but he could
OL,11,Fnot be revived and was pronounced dead
OL,12,Flater that day in hospital.
OL,14,FA small bag was found lodged in his
OL,15,Fairway. The van's CCTV showed that Mr
OL,16,FReardon pushed it into his mouth
OL,17,Fbefore the journey began, having taken
OL,18,Fit from inside his pants while front
OL,19,Fhandcuffed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
