OL,4,Cmisconduct when arrested man died in
OL,5,Cpolice van
OL,7,FPC Mackenzie ` who had worked with
OL,8,FDevon & Cornwall Police for six years
OL,9,F` was dismissed with immediate effect,
OL,10,Fwhile PC Hunkin, who was new in post
OL,11,Fand being mentored at the time, would
OL,12,Falso have been sacked had he not
OL,13,Falready resigned.
OL,15,FBoth have been placed on the College
OL,16,Fof Police's Barred List preventing
OL,17,Fthem from working in policing again in
OL,18,Fthe future.
