OL,3,CPolice officers committed gross
OL,4,Cmisconduct when arrested man died in
OL,5,Cpolice van
OL,7,FIOPC Director Derrick Campbell, said:
OL,8,F"Both officers were first aid trained
OL,9,Fbut neither checked on Mr Reardon or
OL,10,Fprovided any intervention until around
OL,11,F24 minutes after he collapsed onto the
OL,12,Fvan floor.
OL,14,F"Even when the van was stationary at
OL,15,Fthe custody gates, there was still no
OL,16,Furgency on the part of either officer
OL,17,Fto commence first aid, despite them
OL,18,Fbeing aware he'd been unresponsive for
OL,19,Fat least seven minutes.
