OL,7,F"This is a tragic case. I express my
OL,8,Fsincere condolences to the family and
OL,9,Ffriends of Mr Reardon for their loss."
OL,11,FAccording to the IOPC, Devon &
OL,12,FCornwall Police has accepted
OL,13,Frecommendations from the investigation.
OL,15,FThese include reviewing policy and
OL,16,Ftraining relating to the supervision
OL,17,Fof detainees during transportation,
OL,18,Fand reviewing policies and procedures
OL,19,Fin respect of officer mentoring and
OL,20,Ftutoring.
